headline: Intel (INTC) Stays at Hold as Analyst Sees Long Road to Recovery
summary: Intel Corporation (NASDAQ:INTC) is one of the AI Stocks on Wall Street’s Radar. On September 9, Truist Securities analyst William Stein reiterated a Hold rating on the stock with a $21.00 price target following a virtual meeting between Intel and investors.
